                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 2r-81v)&#xD;
- Mangada samāy “Journey to Heaven” (fols. 15rb-19ra)&#xD;
- Homily by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols. 25va-30rb)&#xD;
- Excerpt from Mawāśǝʾt and ʾAryam (fols. 24va-25rb; 48rb-48vb; 55vb-56vb)&#xD;
&#xD;
